summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical distribution easements on portions of Lot 37, Block 6, Lago Vista; Section 2, Township 26 North, Range 3 East, W.M.; Section 8 and 17, Township 26 North Range 4 East, W.M.; Lot 2, King County Short Plat No. 788021; Parcel B, City of Seattle Short Subdivision No. 9003303; Lot 13, Block 8, Hayes Park Addition; Lot 2, Block 3, Fremont Avenue Tracts No. 2; Lot 1, Block 2, Council Crest Division No. 3; Tract 10, Sea Breeze Tract; and placing said easements under the jurisdiction of the City Light Department.
